## Where Content Should Go

- **Progress/status**: Your feedback file (`feedback/{agent}/{YYYY-MM-DD}.md`)
- **Examples**: Inline in [docs/RULES.md](mdc:docs/RULES.md) or relevant runbook
- **Implementation notes**: Manager feedback file
- **Analysis**: Manager feedback file or artifacts/{agent}/ directory

## Enforcement

**Manager audits daily**:
- Root .md files (must be ≤ 6)
- docs/ directory (only allowed patterns)
- Violations → archive to docs/_archive/

**Agents must**:
- Use existing docs structure
- Consolidate into feedback files
- Reference [docs/RULES.md](mdc:docs/RULES.md) for allowed list

**Reference**: [docs/RULES.md](mdc:docs/RULES.md) "No Ad-Hoc Files" section (lines 26-70)

**When in doubt: Use your feedback file, not a new .md file.**
